Step1: 
https://api.dropbox.com:443/1/oauth/request_token?locale=en
setHeader("Authorization", OAuth oauth_version="1.0", oauth_signature_method="PLAINTEXT", oauth_consumer_key="d15asees4r8bw3i", oauth_signature="lkcyv9yf7aybs04&")

Response must contain this:

{oauth_token=sscca3qdjxv14za, oauth_token_secret=7y3yrbynx6wp5ff}
{key="sscca3qdjxv14za", secret="7y3yrbynx6wp5ff"}

Build the authorization url:

https://www.dropbox.com:443/1/oauth/authorize?oauth_token=sscca3qdjxv14za&locale=en

User must go to this url and authorize the application.


Now go to the following url:

https://api.dropbox.com:443/1/oauth/access_token?locale=en
Header: [Authorization: OAuth oauth_version="1.0", oauth_signature_method="PLAINTEXT", oauth_consumer_key="d15asees4r8bw3i", oauth_token="sscca3qdjxv14za", oauth_signature="lkcyv9yf7aybs04&7y3yrbynx6wp5ff"]
The response must contain:
{uid=79237988, oauth_token=rrtm2dma80yrn6r, oauth_token_secret=ffdtsgihcxcoz0s}

Save the uid and the auth tokens above

Now you are prepared to connect to dropbox:


https://api.dropbox.com:443/1/copy_ref/dropbox/tmp?locale=en
[Authorization: OAuth oauth_version="1.0", oauth_signature_method="PLAINTEXT", oauth_consumer_key="d15asees4r8bw3i", oauth_token="rrtm2dma80yrn6r", oauth_signature="lkcyv9yf7aybs04&ffdtsgihcxcoz0s"]
{"links":{"79237988":["rrtm2dma80yrn6r","ffdtsgihcxcoz0s"]},"app_key":["d15asees4r8bw3i","lkcyv9yf7aybs04"]}